 Etinosa Idemudia Etinosa Idemudia is set to welcome her first child with a yet-to-be-identified man. The Nollywood actress made the announcement on Saturday, December 26 by sharing a photo and video of her baby bump. Dressed in a black and gold bedazzled flowing gown, the actress flaunted her baby bump as she described it as the ‘best gift ever’. Sharing the photo of herself cradling her baby bump, she wrote: “This year, I received the best gift ever…..The Gift of Motherhood. I am eternally grateful to God.” View this post on Instagram A post shared by Etinosa Idemudia (@etinosaofficial)